query:
WITH SelectedCountry AS (
                SELECT id
                FROM tb_country
                WHERE name = $4
            ),
            SelectedCity AS (
                SELECT id
                FROM tb_city
                WHERE name = $5
            )
            INSERT INTO tb_article_relavance (article_id, is_related, continent, country_id, city_id) 
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, (SELECT id FROM SelectedCountry), (SELECT id FROM SelectedCity))
            RETURNING id
